  "detailed_description": "Imagine waking up in a Broken world and not being able to remember anything - even know who you are. Hungry zombies roam around the village. You are alone. <br>You need to hide, you need to survive and you need to find the truth.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/f1031ab4f7a7d72da7fc3ebfd35b96f2.avif?t=1642284278\" width=650 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><br>Survive<br>- Search for essential survival items (Food, Water, Batteries...) around the village.<br>- Hide and sneak your way passed Zombies when you don't have enough ammo.<br> Solve Mysteries<br>- Search for codes, hidden messages and secret places.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/9d5d1b450457556a6813b4f82657db59.poster.avif?t=1642284278\" width=650 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/9d5d1b450457556a6813b4f82657db59.webm?t=1642284278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/9d5d1b450457556a6813b4f82657db59.mp4?t=1642284278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- But beware! Not every clue you find will lead you to the right place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/dc5242e815e9585f6afe233ffea83d01.avif?t=1642284278\" width=630 height=340 /></span><br><br><br><u>Warning:</u><br>This game contains intense violence, gore and strong language.",
  "about_the_game": "Imagine waking up in a Broken world and not being able to remember anything - even know who you are. Hungry zombies roam around the village. You are alone. <br>You need to hide, you need to survive and you need to find the truth.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/f1031ab4f7a7d72da7fc3ebfd35b96f2.avif?t=1642284278\" width=650 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><br>Survive<br>- Search for essential survival items (Food, Water, Batteries...) around the village.<br>- Hide and sneak your way passed Zombies when you don't have enough ammo.<br> Solve Mysteries<br>- Search for codes, hidden messages and secret places.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/9d5d1b450457556a6813b4f82657db59.poster.avif?t=1642284278\" width=650 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/9d5d1b450457556a6813b4f82657db59.webm?t=1642284278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/9d5d1b450457556a6813b4f82657db59.mp4?t=1642284278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- But beware! Not every clue you find will lead you to the right place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580440/extras/dc5242e815e9585f6afe233ffea83d01.avif?t=1642284278\" width=630 height=340 /></span><br><br><br><u>Warning:</u><br>This game contains intense violence, gore and strong language.",
